> Using Exclusion_chain

# Tests: Exclusion chain derived tests inferred from 523B policy example in extracted-tests.yaml — 2026-03-27

## Test: drv_001 — 523B example — client gross $3,500 with $20 general exclusion: (3500 - 20 - 65) × 0.5 = $1,707.50

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestDrv001:
  result scope Exclusion_chain.ExclusionChainDecision

scope TestDrv001:
  definition result.gross_earned_income equals $3,500
  definition result.federal_exclusions equals $0
  definition result.eitc_exclusion equals $0
  definition result.irregular_earned_income equals $0
  definition result.student_earned_income equals $0
  definition result.student_monthly_limit equals $0
  definition result.non_needs_based_unearned_remainder equals $20
  definition result.impairment_work_expenses equals $0
  definition result.blind_work_expenses equals $0
  definition result.self_support_exclusion equals $0
  assertion (result.adjusted_earned_income = $1,707.50)
```

